
LONG STORY SHORT

    make configure all

OVERVIEW

    all      - Default; build the compiler, library, and test suite.
    library  - Build the Kitten runtime library.
    compiler - Build the Kitten compiler.
    tests    - Build and run all tests.
    clean    - Delete all build files and start fresh.
    lint     - Run HLint on the Haskell sources.

CONFIGURING

    DEBUG=1   - Build the runtime library or tests with debugging enabled.
    CABAL=... - Set the path to Cabal.

CLEANING

    clean-library  - Delete library build files.
    clean-compiler - Delete compiler build files.
    clean-tests    - Delete test build files.

